				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-23a9d705 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="23a9d705" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p><span id="docs-internal-guid-661c4e84-7fff-fcec-552d-b533a14e2b87"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">For my first job out of college, I was fortunate enough to get a position in the QA department at Naughty Dog working on The Last of Us Part II. I joined the project in the last year of production, so I really had to hit the ground running. Overall working on this game was an amazing opportunity, I was able to work with nearly every department in the studio. It was an amazing experience and I learned so much from the talented people I worked with every day.</span></span></p>					</div>
