				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8f85c6e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="8f85c6e" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>In addition to being responsible for two levels, at the start of 2020 I was made the point of contact for all particles/vfx related issues. My responsibilities included handling all incoming requests from the particles team, as well as performing routine passes on features as they were implemented. A lot of the hard work had already been done by the previous point of contact, but there was still a lot of work left to do!</p><p>This was also an amazing opportunity to work with the particles department, another team of incredibly talented individuals. This area of testing seemed to be something many in QA werenâ€™t as familiar or comfortable with, so it was empowering to become a source of knowledge and help for my coworkers coming across particle issues in their levels.</p>					</div>
